@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <div class="card mt-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>Welcome to the MVC Sports App! We collect basic usage data to ensure our API limits (like sports data from external providers) are managed effectively. If you create an account, we will store your email address and authentication details securely.</p>

            <h3>2. How We Use Your Data</h3>
            <p>Your data is strictly used to provide you with real-time NFL and NBA statistics, game schedules, and team rosters. We do not sell your personal information to third-party marketing companies.</p>

            <h3>3. External APIs</h3>
            <p>This application utilizes SportsData.io to fetch live statistics. By using this application, you also agree to their respective privacy guidelines regarding data retrieval.</p>

            <h3>4. Contact Us</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact our development team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>